<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no" />
  <title>老兵电子中心 | Veteran Electronics Hub</title>
</head>
<body class="bg-zinc-950 text-zinc-100 font-mono min-h-screen pb-32" style="background-color: #09090b !important; color: #f4f4f5 !important; font-family: monospace !important; min-h: 100vh !important; padding-bottom: 120px !important;">

  <nav class="p-6 max-w-6xl mx-auto flex justify-between items-center" style="border-b: 1px solid #27272a !important; display: flex !important; justify-content: space-between !important; align-items: center !important;">
    <div style="color: #f59e0b !important; font-size: 1.25rem !important; font-weight: bold !important;">VETERAN.CORE //</div>
    <div style="display: flex !important; align-items: center !important; gap: 16px !important;">
      <span style="color: #f59e0b !important; font-weight: bold !important; font-size: 14px !important;">中文</span>
      <span style="color: #3f3f46 !important;">|</span>
      <a href="/bom-hub" style="background-color: #f59e0b !important; color: #09090b !important; padding: 6px 16px !important; font-weight: bold !important; text-decoration: none !important;">BOM HUB</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <header style="text-align: center !important; padding-top: 5rem !important; padding-bottom: 4rem !important; max-w: 56rem !important; margin: 0 auto !important; padding-left: 1.5rem !important; padding-right: 1.5rem !important;"> 
    <h1 style="font-size: 2.5rem !important; font-weight: 900 !important; line-height: 1.2 !important; margin-bottom: 1.5rem !important;">
      不要只是采购元器件。<br/>
      <span style="color: #f59e0b !important;">用 22 年硬件行业经验，帮您优化每一颗芯片。</span>
    </h1>
    <p style="color: #a1a1aa !important; max-w: 42rem !important; margin: 0 auto !important; font-size: 1rem !important;">[坐标：深圳] // 为全球工程师提供独立分析、品质标准和战略元器件优化。</p>
  </header>

  <main style="max-w: 72rem !important; margin: 0 auto !important; padding: 0 1.5rem !important; display: grid !important; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)) !important; gap: 1.5rem !important;">
    <div style="background-color: #18181b !important; padding: 2rem !important; border: 1px solid #27272a !important;">
      <div style="color: #f59e0b !important; font-size: 0.75rem !important; font-weight: bold !important; margin-bottom: 1rem !important;">// MODULE_01</div>
      <h2 style="font-size: 1.25rem !important; font-weight: bold !important; margin-bottom: 0.75rem !important;">国产 vs 全球</h2>
      <p style="color: #a1a1aa !important; font-size: 0.875rem !important; line-height: 1.5 !important;">深度可靠性测试、交叉参考分析，以及国产替代方案与一线品牌的真实对比。</p>
    </div>

    <div style="background-color: #18181b !important; padding: 2rem !important; border: 1px solid #27272a !important;">
      <div style="color: #f59e0b !important; font-size: 0.75rem !important; font-weight: bold !important; margin-bottom: 1rem !important;">// MODULE_02</div>
      <h2 style="font-size: 1.25rem !important; font-weight: bold !important; margin-bottom: 0.75rem !important;">BOM 优化</h2>
      <p style="color: #a1a1aa !important; font-size: 0.875rem !important; line-height: 1.5 !important;">不降低品质的成本降低策略。生命周期管理和供应链风险缓解指南。</p>
    </div>

    <div style="background-color: #18181b !important; padding: 2rem !important; border: 1px solid #27272a !important;">
      <div style="color: #f59e0b !important; font-size: 0.75rem !important; font-weight: bold !important; margin-bottom: 1rem !important;">// MODULE_03</div>
      <h2 style="font-size: 1.25rem !important; font-weight: bold !important; margin-bottom: 0.75rem !important;">关于我</h2>
      <p style="color: #a1a1aa !important; font-size: 0.875rem !important; line-height: 1.5 !important;">2004 年扎根深圳，22 年电子元器件采购老兵。您在市场上的透明耳目。</p>
    </div>
  </main>

  <div style="position: fixed !important; bottom: 0 !important; left: 0 !important; right: 0 !important; background-color: rgba(24, 24, 27, 0.98) !important; border-top: 1px solid #27272a !important; padding: 12px 0 !important; display: flex !important; justify-content: space-around !important; align-items: center !important; z-index: 999999 !important; height: 65px !important;">
    <a href="/" style="text-decoration: none !important; display: flex !important; flex-direction: column !important; align-items: center !important; gap: 2px !important; color: #f59e0b !important;">
      <svg style="width: 24px !important; height: 24px !important;" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 12l2-2m0 0l7-7 7 7M5 10v10a1 1 0 001 1h3m10-11l2 2m-2-2v10a1 1 0 01-1 1h-3m-6 0a1 1 0 001-1v-4a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v4a1 1 0 001 1m-6 0h6"></path></svg>
      <span style="font-size: 11px !important; font-weight: bold !important;">HOME / 主页</span>
    </a>
    
    <a href="/bom-hub" style="text-decoration: none !important; display: flex !important; flex-direction: column !important; align-items: center !important; gap: 2px !important; color: #a1a1aa !important;">
      <svg style="width: 24px !important; height: 24px !important;" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-3 7h3m-3 4h3m-6-4h.01M9 16h.01"></path></svg>
      <span style="font-size: 11px !important; font-weight: bold !important;">BOM HUB</span>
    </a>
  </div>

</body>
</html>